heading_context: Log in to tied and rebated oils excise services
chunks.html_content:
Log in to the following HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) excise services for dealers in tied and rebated (controlled) oils:

  • Rebated Oils Enquiry Service
  • Rebated Oils Returns Internet Upload Service
  • Tied Oil Enquiry Service

chunks.html_content: Online services may be slow during busy times. Check if there are any problems with the rebated oils or tied oils services.

heading_context: Log in to tied and rebated oils excise services
chunks.html_content:
These services are for registered dealers in rebated (controlled) oils and tied oils to submit returns and check customers’ approval numbers.

You’ll need a Government Gateway user ID and password to access these services. If you do not have a user ID, you can create one when you sign in for the first time. Your organisation must be approved under the relevant scheme when you create a user ID.
